--------------------------------------------------------------------------
CASTLE CODE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
This policy is to let any and all that code here know that anything
that you code here becomes a part of DarkWind.  All code that is
generated on DarkWind is considered to be a part of a communal effort
to make DarkWind better.  What this means is, if you code an area here
on DarkWind, first, we want that area to be unique to DarkWind and not
running on other muds as well as here, and second, if you decide to
leave DarkWind, your castle stays with this mud.  If you leave, your
code can and will continue to be used here as long as the administration
feels that it is a benefit to the mud as a whole.  If you choose to leave,
we will most likely NOT provide you with a copy of your area unless at
least one of the following factors are present: One, your area was never
opened here on DarkWind, Two, the administration of DarkWind feels that
the loss of your area won't have a detrimental effect on the Mud, or Three,
the administration feels confindent that you only want the code for archival
reasons and have no intentions of putting the code up on another mud at
least for the time it is being used on DarkWind.  Even if one or more of the
above conditions are met, this does not guarantee you will get a copy, it
is still up to the administration to decide this.  While this policy may
seem a little harsh, it is written this way so that there is no way a
person can come back later and state that they didnt understand our policy
on this matter.
 
